Notes:
On 7-27-77 Dire Straits recorded the following Demos:
Wild West End, Sultans of Swing, Down To The Waterline,
Sacred Loving and Water of Love.  

In October they recorded: Southbound Again, In The Gallery
& Six Blade Knife for BBC Radio London.

On 11-09-77 they recorded the following Demos:
Setting Me Up, Eastbound Train & Real Girl.
